data.description: Motivated Seller bring us an offer! *****Outdoor paradise on a sandy beach on the Little Tchefuncte River.  Offers 3 bedrooms 3.5 baths plus study/office/4th bedroom, soaring ceilings throughout.  Large den of kitchen with fireplace, wall of windows with spectacular views.  Formal living has custom bookshelves, fireplace and french doors leading to back deck overlooking the river.  Exceptional kitchen with custom cabinets, tons of storage, ample counterspace, granite, tiled backsplash, center island with gas cooktop, stainless appliances, double oven, wine cooler and huge walk-in pantry.  Cozy primary suite has a fireplace, a sitting area w/a serene view, french doors leading to back deck and 2 walk-in closets. Lavish primary bath has hydro tub, dual sinks and separate shower.  2 bedrooms, each having private full baths upstairs.  Open area under house for parking or entertaining.  Tons of amenities including a lift to bring up groceries, amazing raised workshop, bamboo flooring and 24" tile, house plumbed for gas and much more!  New roof installed in 2020!  Vacation all year round on this stunning, private and breathtaking 7.5+/- acre property.  A must see!
